            {
              "type": "module",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "module-body",
                  "html": "<p>English is one of the few languages that allows gender ambiguity (for example, &#x201C;you can see their picture&#x201D;). Most other languages must be more specific (&#x201C;you can see his or her picture,&#x201D; for example). </p><p>Be specific about gender whenever possible (his, her, and so on).</p>"
